ed="T" n="0816a19"/><persName key="A010510">釋唯儼</persName>，俗姓<name>寒</name><ptr target="#n2241"/>，<placeName key="PL000000005051">絳縣</placeName><ptr target="#n1850"/>人也。童齓慷愷<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1094"/>，敏俊逸<lb
ed="T" n="0816a20"/>群。<date key="j19990541999348" from-iso="+0761-02-14" to-iso="+0761-12-05">年十七</date>，<choice resp="makita"><sic>從</sic><corr>徙</corr></choice><placeName key="PL000000019114">南康</placeName>事<placeName key="PL000000031787"><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>湖</sic><corr>潮</corr></choice>陽</placeName>西山<ptr target="#n496"/><persName key="A011917"><anchor xml:id="beg0816001"/>慧照<anchor xml:id="end0816001"/><roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>。<lb
ed="T" n="0816a21"/><date from-iso="+0773-02-01" key="j20034242003806" to-iso="+0774-02-18"><name>大曆</name>八年</date>，納戒于<placeName key="PL000000028989">衡嶽寺</placeName><persName key="A010470">希<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>澡</sic><corr>操</corr></choice><roleName>律師</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n497"/>所，乃曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0816a22"/>「大丈夫當離法自淨，焉能屑屑事細行於布<lb
ed="T" n="0816a23"/>巾邪？<ptr target="#n498"/>」遂謁<persName key="A010291">石頭<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，密證心法，住<placeName key="PL000000028895">藥山</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0816a24"/>焉。一夜明月，陟彼崔嵬<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1352"/>，大笑一聲，聲應<placeName key="PL000000029560">澧陽</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0816a25"/>東九十許里。其夜<placeName key="PL000000029560">澧陽</placeName>人皆聞其聲，盡云是<lb
ed="T" n="0816a26"/>東家，明辰展轉尋問，迭互推尋，直至<placeName key="PL000000028895">藥山</placeName>，徒<lb
ed="T" n="0816a27"/>眾云：「昨夜<ref type="person" target="#A010510">和尚</ref><ref type="place" target="#PL000000028895">山</ref>頂大笑是歟？」自茲振譽，遐<lb
ed="T" n="0816a28"/>邇喧然。<date notBefore-iso="+0806-01-29" key="j20154742020606" notAfter-iso="+0820-02-17"><name>元和</name>中</date><persName key="A010395">李翱</persName>為考功員外郎，與<persName key="A011919">李景<lb
ed="T" n="0816a29"/>儉</persName>相善。<persName key="A011919">儉</persName>除諫議，<anchor xml:id="beg0816sgsz2"/>薦<anchor xml:id="end0816sgsz2"/><persName key="A010395">翱</persName>自代，及<persName key="A011919">儉</persName>獲譴，<persName key="A010395">翱</persName><pb ed="T" n="0816b" xml:id="T50.2061.0816b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0816b01"/>乃坐此出為<placeName key="PL000000029413">朗州</placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0816sgsz3"/>刺<anchor xml:id="end0816sgsz3"/>史<ptr target="#n2242"/>。<persName key="A010395">翱</persName>閑來謁<persName key="A010510">儼</persName>，遂成<lb
ed="T" n="0816b02"/>警悟。又初見<persName key="A010510">儼</persName>，執經卷不顧，侍者白曰：「太<lb
ed="T" n="0816b03"/>守在此。」<persName key="A010395">翱</persName>性褊急，乃倡言曰：「見面不似聞<lb
ed="T" n="0816b04"/>名。」<persName key="A010510">儼</persName>乃呼，<persName key="A010395">翱</persName>應唯，曰：「太守何貴耳賤目？」<persName key="A010395">翱</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0816b05"/>拱手謝之，問曰：「何謂道邪？」<persName key="A010510">儼</persName>指天指淨<lb
ed="T" n="0816b06"/>瓶曰：「雲在青天水在瓶。」<persName key="A010395">翱</persName>于時暗室已明，<lb
ed="T" n="0816b07"/>疑氷頓泮，尋有偈云：「<anchor xml:id="beg0816002"/>鍊<anchor xml:id="end0816002"/>得身形似鶴形，<lb
ed="T" n="0816b08"/>千株松下兩函經。我來相問<ptr target="#n499"/>無餘說，雲在青<lb
ed="T" n="0816b09"/>天水在瓶。」又偈「選得幽居愜野情，終年<lb
ed="T" n="0816b10"/>無送亦無迎。有時直上孤峯頂，月下披雲<lb
ed="T" n="0816b11"/>笑一聲。<ptr target="#n2243"/>」初<persName key="A010395">翱</persName>與<persName key="A003947">韓愈</persName>、<persName key="A003970">柳宗元</persName>、<persName key="A006962">劉禹錫</persName>為文會<lb
ed="T" n="0816b12"/>之交，自相與述古言、法《六<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>藉</sic><corr>籍</corr></choice>》<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1095"/>，為文黜浮華、<lb
ed="T" n="0816b13"/>尚理致，言為文者<persName key="A003947">韓</persName>、<persName key="A003970">柳</persName>、<persName key="A006962">劉</persName>焉。<persName key="A003947">吏部</persName>常論：「<persName key="A002174">仲<lb
ed="T" n="0816b14"/>尼</persName>既沒，諸子異端，故<persName key="A011920">荀</persName><persName key="A004486">孟</persName>復之，<persName key="A006982">楊</persName><persName key="A006931">墨</persName>之流洗<lb
ed="T" n="0816b15"/>然遺落。殆<date from-iso="+0557-02-17" key="j19245481933331" to-iso="+0581-03-06">周</date><date from-iso="+0581-03-06" key="j19333311946884" to-iso="+0618-04-15">隋</date>之世，王道弗興，故<persName key="A011186">文中子</persName>有<lb
ed="T" n="0816b16"/>作，應在乎諸子左右<ptr target="#n2244"/>。<placeName key="PL000000000106">唐</placeName>興，<persName key="A002115">房</persName><persName key="A020014">魏</persName>既亡，失道<lb
ed="T" n="0816b17"/>尚華，至有<persName key="A002099">武后</persName>之弊，<persName key="A008454">安</persName><persName key="A010333">史</persName>之殘。<ref type="person" target="#A003947">吾</ref>約二三<lb
ed="T" n="0816b18"/>子同致君復<persName key="A002433">堯</persName><persName key="A002434">舜</persName>之道，不可放清言而廢<lb
ed="T" n="0816b19"/><name>儒</name>，縱<name>梵</name>書而猾<placeName key="PL000000000083">夏</placeName><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1142"/>。敢有邪心歸<name>釋</name>氏者，<lb
ed="T" n="0816b20"/>有渝此盟，無享人爵，無永天年。先聖明<lb
ed="T" n="0816b21"/>神，是糺是殛！<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1146"/>」無何<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g493"/>，<persName key="A010395">翱</persName>邂逅於<persName key="A010510">儼</persName>，頓了本心。<lb
ed="T" n="0816b22"/>末由戶部尚書、<placeName key="PL000000027118">襄州</placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0816sgsz4"/>刺<anchor xml:id="end0816sgsz4"/>史，充<placeName key="PL000000027117">山南東道</placeName>節<lb
ed="T" n="0816b23"/>度使<ptr target="#n2245"/>。復遇<persName key="A010391">紫玉<roleName>禪翁</roleName></persName>，且增明道趣，著《復性<lb
ed="T" n="0816b24"/>書》上下二篇<ptr target="#n2246"/>。大抵謂：本性明白，為六情<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1147"/>玷污，<lb
ed="T" n="0816b25"/>迷而不返，今牽復之，猶地雷之復見天地<lb
ed="T" n="0816b26"/>心矣！即內教之返本還源也<ptr target="#n2247"/>。其書露而且<lb
ed="T" n="0816b27"/>隱，蓋而又彰，其文則〈象〉、〈繫〉、〈中庸〉，隱而不援<name>釋</name><lb
ed="T" n="0816b28"/>教；其理則從真捨妄，彰而乃顯自心。弗事<lb
ed="T" n="0816b29"/>言陳，唯萌意許也。<persName key="A003947">韓</persName><persName key="A003970">柳</persName>覽之，歎曰：「吾道萎<pb ed="T" n="0816c" xml:id="T50.2061.0816c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0816c01"/>遲，<persName key="A010395">翱</persName>且逃矣！」<persName key="A010510">儼</persName>陶鍊難化，護法功多，迴是<lb
ed="T" n="0816c02"/>子之心，拔山扛鼎，猶或云易。又相國<persName key="A010468">崔群</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0816c03"/>常侍<persName key="A011921">溫造</persName>相繼問道，<persName key="A010510">儼</persName>能開發道意。以<date from-iso="+0828-01-25" key="j20235052023888" to-iso="+0829-02-11"><name>大和</name><lb
ed="T" n="0816c04"/>二年</date><ptr target="#n500"/>將欲終，告眾曰：「法堂即頹矣。」皆不喻<lb
ed="T" n="0816c05"/>旨，率人以長木而枝柱之，<persName key="A010510">儼</persName>撫掌大笑<lb
ed="T" n="0816c06"/>云：「都未曉<ref type="person" target="#A010510">吾</ref>意。」合掌而寂，春秋七十云<ptr target="#n501"/>。</p><p xml:id="pT50p0816c0701"><lb
ed="T" n="0816c07"/>系曰：甞覽<persName key="A010395">李文<roleName>公</roleName></persName>《復性》二篇，明佛理不引<lb
ed="T" n="0816c08"/>佛書，援證而徵，取《易》《禮》而止。可謂外柔順而<lb
ed="T" n="0816c09"/>內剛逆也，故曰「得象而忘言<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1149"/>」矣！經云治世<lb
ed="T" n="0816c10"/><anchor xml:id="beg0816003"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>語</sic><corr>諸</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0816003"/>言皆成正法者<ptr target="#n2248"/>，<persName key="A010395">李<roleName>公</roleName></persName>有焉。<persName key="A010510">儼<roleName>公</roleName></persName>一笑，聲<lb
ed="T" n="0816c11"/>徹遐鄉，雖未勞<persName key="A000053">目連</persName>遠尋，而《易例》有諸：「隆<lb
ed="T" n="0816c12"/>墀永歎，遠壑必盈<ptr target="#n2249"/>」，道感如然不知其然也！</p>
